               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-222" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-222" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-222" type="surname" value="LONG"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-222" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS LONG</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Philpot-lane. I was present when Mrs. Long gave the prisoner 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I will not swear he is the man—a man brought some shoes on that day, and on the Saturday previous.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How do you know Mrs. Long gave me 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I heard you say they came to 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and I saw her give you money.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-223" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-223" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-223" type="surname" value="BIGGS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-223" type="given" value="EVAN"></interp>EVAN BIGGS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am foreman to Mr. Thomas Bowtell, a shoemaker in Cheapside. The prisoner was shopman there—I sent him with some shoes to Mr. Long, on Saturday the 11th of January, and on Saturday the 18th, he took another pair—the two pairs came to 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., but he was to leave them if he did not have the money—when he came back, I said, "Did Mrs. Long pay you?"—he said, "No, but you are to send the bill on Tuesday morning "—I sent the bill then, and found he had received it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-224" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-224" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-224" type="surname" value="LONG"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-224" type="given" value="JOHN POLLOCK"></interp>JOHN POLLOCK LONG</persName>
                  </hi>. I was at home on the 18th of January—the prisoner came with the shoes—I saw some silver paid him—how much I cannot say—there were some shillings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How could you see Mrs. Long pay me any money, when you were laughing and hiding by the table? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> We were looking just over the table.</p>
               <p>
