                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. I saw somebody paid—he asked for 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I said to Mrs. Long, "Have you enough silver?"—she said she had—I cannot say whether it was shillings or half-crowns that were paid.</p>
